      "y": 125,
      "width": 305,
      "height": 110,
      "text": "Angle = |30H - 5.5M|\n\nH = hour (12-hr format)\nM = minutes\n\nIf result > 180 -> Angle = 360 - result\n(always take the SMALLER angle)",
