      "originalText": "             12 hrs | 24 hrs\nOverlap(0):    11   |   22   (NOT 12/24!)\nRight(90):     22   |   44\nStraight(180): 11   |   22   (NOT 12/24!)\nAny theta:     22   |   44\n\nTime between overlaps = 12/11 hr = 65min 27sec",
