    {
      "id": "el_26",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 579,
      "width": 274,
      "height": 216,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Hr hand = 30×4 + 0.5×30 = 135°\n  Min hand = 6×30 = 180°\nStep 2: Angle = |135-180| = 45°\n\nTRICK:\nAngle = |30H - 5.5M|\n= |30(4) - 5.5(30)| = |120-165| = 45°\n\n     12\n  9   .    3\n  8  / 45°  4 ← hour\n     6 ← min\n\nAnswer: 45 degrees ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
