      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Hr hand = 30×4 + 0.5×30 = 135°\n  Min hand = 6×30 = 180°\nStep 2: Angle = |135-180| = 45°\n\nTRICK:\nAngle = |30H - 5.5M|\n= |30(4) - 5.5(30)| = |120-165| = 45°\n\n     12\n  9   .    3\n  8  / 45°  4 ← hour\n     6 ← min\n\nAnswer: 45 degrees ✓",
