      "type": "text",
      "x": 535,
      "y": 595,
      "width": 245,
      "height": 188,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: M = (30H ± 90) × 2/11, H=3\n  Case 1: (90+90)×2/11 = 32 8/11\n  Case 2: (90-90)×2/11 = 0\n\nTRICK:\nPlug H and theta into formula\nTwo answers (± gives 2 cases)\nReject if M<0 or M>=60\n\n  3:00 (90°) and 3:32 8/11 (90°)\n\nAnswer: 3:00 and 3:32 8/11 min ✓",
