      "y": 595,
      "width": 296,
      "height": 159,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: M = (30H ± 180) × 2/11, H=2\n  Case 1: (60+180)×2/11 = 43 7/11 OK\n  Case 2: (60-180)×2/11 = negative REJECT\n\nTRICK:\n180° usually gives only ONE solution\n(other case goes negative)\nOnly exception: 6 o'clock range\n\nAnswer: 2:43 7/11 min ✓",
