      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: 12 hours → 11 overlaps\n  (11→12 overlap IS next 12:00)\nStep 2: 24 hours → 22 overlaps\n\nTRICK:\nOverlaps: 11 per 12hr, 22 per 24hr\nGap = 12/11 hr = 65 min 27 sec\nNOT 12/24 because hands share 12:00!\n\nAnswer: 22 times in 24 hours ✓",
