      "x": 1005,
      "y": 945,
      "width": 288,
      "height": 188,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Expected 12×2=24\n  But 2 merge at 3:00 and 9:00\nStep 2: Actual = 24-2 = 22 in 12hr\n\nTRICK:\n  Angle  | 12 hrs | 24 hrs\n  0°     |   11   |   22\n  90°    |   22   |   44\n  180°   |   11   |   22\n  any θ  |   22   |   44\n\nAnswer: 22 times (12h), 44 times (24h) ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
