      "width": 288,
      "height": 159,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Expected 12 (once per hour)\n  But 1 merges at 6:00\nStep 2: Actual = 12-1 = 11 in 12hr\n\nTRICK:\n180° count = same as overlap count = 11\n5→6 and 6→7 slots share the 6:00 event\nIn 24hr = 22\n\nAnswer: 11 times (12h), 22 times (24h) ✓",
