      "type": "text",
      "x": 535,
      "y": 1283,
      "width": 216,
      "height": 173,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: 3:15 → |30(3)-5.5(15)|\n  = |90-82.5| = 7.5°\nStep 2: 7:20 → |30(7)-5.5(20)|\n  = |210-110| = 100°\n\nTRICK:\nAngle = |30H - 5.5M|\nTRAP: 3:15 is NOT 0°!\nHour hand moves past 3 by 7.5°\n\nAnswer: (a) 7.5° (b) 100° ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
