      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Elapsed = 12 hours\n  Gain = 5×12 = 60 min = 1 hr\nStep 2: Clock = 8PM + 1hr = 9PM\n\nTRICK:\nGains → FAST → shows MORE\nLoses → SLOW → shows LESS\nClock = actual ± (rate × hours)\n\nAnswer: 9:00 PM ✓",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
