      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 1624,
      "width": 274,
      "height": 159,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Diff/hr = 3+2 = 5 min/hr\n  Same time when diff = 720 min\nStep 2: Time = 720/5 = 144 hr = 6 days\n\nTRICK:\nTwo clocks: 720/(gain+loss) hours\nSingle clock: 720/rate hours\n720 = 12 hours in minutes\n\nAnswer: After 6 days (144 hours) ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
