      "y": 1608,
      "width": 274,
      "height": 173,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Mirror = 11:60 - actual\n  = 11:60 - 3:20\nStep 2: = 8:40\n\nTRICK:\nMirror = (11-H):(60-M)\n3:20 → 8:40 | 1:50 → 10:10\n4:15 → 7:45 | 12:00 → 12:00\nSpecial: 12:00 and 6:00 same in mirror\n\nAnswer: 8:40 ✓",
