      "x": 1005,
      "y": 1608,
      "width": 267,
      "height": 173,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: M = (30H ± θ)×2/11, H=7, θ=60\n  Case 1: (210+60)×2/11 = 49 1/11\n  Case 2: (210-60)×2/11 = 27 3/11\n  Both valid (0 ≤ M < 60)\n\nTRICK:\nPlug into formula, get 2 answers\n+θ = min hand ahead of hour hand\n-θ = min hand behind hour hand\n\nAnswer: 7:27 3/11 and 7:49 1/11 ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
